@startuml UC11_ReviewCourseDrafts
title UC11 - Review Course Drafts
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fredoslav2004/MinimalThemePUML/refs/heads/main/minimal-theme.puml

actor Admin
participant System

Admin -> System: Request pending drafts
System --> Admin: Display list of drafts awaiting review
Admin -> System: Select draft to review
System --> Admin: Show draft details
alt Approve
    Admin -> System: Approve draft
    System -> System: Update status to approved and initialize new course
    System --> Admin: Confirm approval
else Disapprove
    Admin -> System: Disapprove draft
    System -> System: Delete the draft
    System --> Admin: Confirm rejection
end
@enduml
